HEADWORD: Cleanness
<hw>Clean"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS. <ets>cl<?/nnes</ets>. See
<er>Clean</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The state or quality of being
